spanGrp.span: The story of Mumu and Kotkot, it is not an empty story, it is a story that is still alive.
050-001 Natrauswen ni Mumu go Kotkot , ga ita pi natrauswen p̃al mau , ga ipi natrauswen nen im̃ool .
So Mumu and Kotkot used to walk around Vanuatu.
§ 050-002 Taos Mumu go Kotkot gar rato siwer usrek ki nlaun nig Vanuatu .
§ 050-003 Pan pak Banks pan pan kaimer ler mai pak Aneityum rato siwer tefla .
§ 050-004 Me san kin ratkos ga ratok naur nig Etgo go Em̃ae .
§ 050-006 Go sernrak rato ipitlak napu negar iur esa .
§ 050-007 Kin imai kin iteflan panpanpan ileg pan .
§ 050-008 Ur ntas kin ipanpan pak Ermag , pak
Tanna , pak Aneityum . Kaimer ler mai .
§ 050-009 Go gar rapi tenen kin ratu teflan welkia ratok lek natam̃ol
, § 050-010 naat nen ipreg nawesien sa go rakfo watgi .
§ 050-013 Me tete nrak rapregi nen kin kefo mat .
